ArmySurplus.story:
//--UES CONTACT LIGHT CARGO MANIFEST --//

Item: Army Surplus Kit, Type C
Purpose: increase the survivability of autonomous units
Condition: decommissioned, restored, decommissioned again, restored again
Compatibility: partial

Container contents:

reinforced hull plates;
repair braces;
emergency power adapter;
field medical distributor;
infantry-unit manual;
repair-drone manual;
a sheet of corrections explaining why these are the same manual.

Logistics note:
If the restoration system cannot distinguish a soldier from a drone, do not fix it until the operation is over.
